  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Les Melezes is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each day a continental breakfast buffet is served with a variety of sweet and savoury options. </p>
<p>During the evening, you can enjoy a four course set menu consisting of fresh market produce. </p>
<p>Christmas and New Years gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
